headline: State Street Corporation Declares Dividends on its Common Stock and Non-Cumulative Perpetual Preferred Stock Series “G,” “I,” and “J”
summary: State Street Corporation today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.76 per share of common stock, payable on April 11, 2025 to common shareholders of record at the close of business on April 1,...
